item.title: CVE-2018-1435|2024-09-17T01:31:06.993Z -- ibm -- notes
item.description: IBM Notes 8.5 and 9.0 is vulnerable to a DLL hijacking attack. A remote attacker could trick a user to double click a malicious executable in an attacker-controlled directory, which could result in code execution. IBM X-Force ID: 139563.
